---
description: src/rag/application/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---
## Queries
- Must be immutable
- No side effects

---

## Handlers
- One public method: execute()
- One handler per use case
- Must use DI via Port tokens
- No framework types (Request, Response)
- No infrastructure types (Prisma, SDKs)

---

## Services
- Orchestration only
- No business logic
- Use only Ports

---

## Data
- Return DTOs only
- Never return domain entities

---

## Dependencies
Allowed:
- Ports (interfaces)
- DTOs
- Commands / Queries

Forbidden:
- Prisma / DB clients
- External SDKs
- NestJS Request/Response

---

## Anti-Patterns
- Mixing command + query
- Business logic in handlers
- Direct infra usage
- Framework decorators in commands/queries